        <prompt>What was Jane Addams' Hull House?</prompt>
        <options>
            <option letter="a">A factory</option>
            <option letter="b">A settlement house</option>
            <option letter="c">A prison</option>
            <option letter="d">A church</option>
        </options>
        <answer>b</answer>
        <explanation>Hull House was a settlement house in Chicago founded by Jane Addams to help immigrants adjust to American life and improve their living conditions.</explanation>
    </question>

